FOR THIS SECTION, only use those HERITAGE subjects who have VO2max and proteomic data measured at baseline and after exercise training (N=643)

Update 03/18/2024 : Scale protein score.

mean_pre_score_unscaled <- mean(protein_score_pre$proteomic_score_pre)
sd_pre_score_unscaled <- sd(protein_score_pre$proteomic_score_pre)

protein_score_pre_scaled = 
  protein_score_pre %>% 
  transmute(PID, proteomic_score_pre_scaled = (proteomic_score_pre - mean_pre_score_unscaled) / sd_pre_score_unscaled)

protein_score_post_scaled = 
  protein_score_post %>% 
  transmute(PID, proteomic_score_post_scaled = (proteomic_score_post - mean_pre_score_unscaled) / sd_pre_score_unscaled)

protein_score_prepost_scaled  = 
  protein_score_pre_scaled %>% 
  inner_join(protein_score_post_scaled, by = "PID")
her_pheno_lt = her_pheno_raw %>% 
  mutate(SEX  = case_when(SEX ==  1 ~ "Male", SEX == 2 ~ "Female", TRUE ~ NA_character_),
         RACE = case_when(RACE == 1 ~ "Black", RACE == 2 ~ "Caucasian", TRUE ~ NA_character_),
         GEN  = case_when(GEN ==  1 ~ "Parent", GEN == 2 ~ "Offspring", TRUE ~ NA_character_),
         B_VO2MX_B_WT18 = B_VO2MX/B_WT18,
         P_VO2MX_P_WT18 = P_VO2MX/P_WT18,
         D_VO2MX_ML_KG_MIN = P_VO2MX/P_WT18 - B_VO2MX/B_WT18
         ) %>% 
  select(PID, SEX, RACE, AGE, GEN, B_BMI, B_VO2MX, D_VO2MX, B_WT18, D_WT18, P_VO2MX, P_WT18, B_VO2MX_B_WT18, P_VO2MX_P_WT18, D_VO2MX_ML_KG_MIN) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(B_VO2MX), !is.na(B_BMI), !is.na(AGE), !is.na(SEX), !is.na(B_WT18)) %>%  #, 
  mutate(SEX = factor(SEX, levels = c("Male", "Female")))

part_2_df = her_pheno_lt %>% inner_join(protein_score_prepost, by = "PID")

part_2_df_scaled = her_pheno_lt %>% inner_join(protein_score_prepost_scaled, by = "PID")
